"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block doa drugH1Div\" id=\"F161962\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Dosing: Adult",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Cardiac decompensation: I.V. infusion: 2.5-20 mcg/kg/minute; maximum: 40 mcg/kg/minute, titrate to desired response; see table.",
